  41               	xevious_sub_irq:
  42               	    *** these are ordinarily called from the main SUB routine
  43               	    *** because there is not interrupt context in SUB
  44               	    *** - calls these from the MAIN IRQ instead
  45               	    *** - try swapping the order to reduce 'shaking'
  46               	    ***   of ground objects
  47               	    ****jbsr       sub_fn_0__update_32_sprite_hw
  48 0026 303C 0020 	    move.w    #32,d0                            | start at sprite 32
